title: TELLING IT LIKE IT IS NEWBORN CARE CLASS FOR FIRST TIME PARENTS TO BE
desc: Join Yvette Humphrey, one of New York's Premier Baby Nurses, with 39 years of experience caring for newborns, as she reveals w hat professionals know but do not tell you about what bringing your baby home is really like, Yvette  offers practical advice to first-time parents. She will provide you with the skills you need to care for your newborn during the first two months of life. Also join other first time moms and dads who will share their stories.
